          </span>
          <a href="/track-record?from=landing" style={{ fontSize: mobile ? 13 : 13.5, color: 'var(--accent, var(--mint))', textDecoration: 'none', fontFamily: 'var(--font-mono)', whiteSpace: 'nowrap' }}>
            See the live track record →
          </a>
        </div>
        <div style={{ display: 'flex', flexWrap: 'wrap', alignItems: 'center', gap: mobile ? 10 : 12 }}>
          <a href="https://basescan.org/address/0x6485396ac981fe0a58540dfbf3e730f6f7bcbf81" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style={badge}>
            🔗 On-Chain Verified
